descriptionMarkdown:
This Particular Blueprint Auto Requests whatever AAI Programmable Vehicle you put in requester chest and Deploys it up to 5 of that unit Until the value of that particular unit is Greater then 4
Requestor Chest = (UNIT)
Top Right Combinator = (Quantity of type Signal < 4 OUTPUT 1 of whatever signal) this can be changed.
signal goes to inserter and configure inserter to activate until signal is cleared Reads Content of Vehicle Deployer chest
The Arithmetic combinator and Decider Combinator are looped thru unit scanner and you would configure what unit you want it to count there
Arithmetic Settings Unit ID signal + 1 OUTPUT Unit ID Input to Unit Scanner Outputs to Decider Combinator Unit ID < Quantity Of Type Signal Outputs UNIT ID to Arithmetic Combinator
title: Additional BluePrints For AAI
